ery%20to%20gaze%20at.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screen%20in%20ceiling%20of%20train%20interior%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717bd1b01ea6d83dee3207e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222413%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20the%20onboard%20speedometer%20clocked%20334.7%20kilometers%20per%20hour.%20%3Cp%3EEmily%20Garnham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20don't%20expect%20to%20see%20beautiful%20scenery%20on%20this%20journey%20because%20it%20goes%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurotunnel-le-shuttle-train-passengers-trapped-hours-terrifying-undersea-tunnel-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eundersea%20railway%20tunnel%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20links%20England%20and%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20only%20spent%2020%20minutes%20below%20ground%20in%20the%20Channel%20Tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20the%20green%20Kent%20countryside%2C%20expansive%20French%20farmland%20past%20Calais%2C%20and%20the%20industrial%20%26quot%3Bvistas%26quot%3B%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20onboard%20food%20offerings%20exceeded%20all%20our%20expectations.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tray%20of%20food%2C%20water%2C%20napkin%20on%20train%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717bd1b01ea6d83dee3207f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20meals%20didn't%20look%20amazing%20but%20they%20had%20tons%20of%20flavor.%20%3Cp%3EEmily%20Garnham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20food%20and%20drinks%20were%20served%20minutes%20after%20we'd%20started%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20meal%20was%20included%20in%20our%20mid-tier%20rail%20fare%2C%20but%20standard%20passengers%20can%20buy%20food%20and%20drinks%20on%20board.%20Premier%20passengers%20can%20expect%20fine%20dining%20%E2%80%94%20think%20three-course%20meals%20with%20bubbly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I've%20seen%20too%20many%20airplane%20meals%20that%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20designed%20for%20deep-space%20explorations%2C%20I%20had%20low%20expectations%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Blight%20meal%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20be%20served%20on%20the%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20was%20really%20pleasantly%20surprised.%20The%20menu%20changes%20seasonally%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurostar.com%2Fus-en%2Fsustainability%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Eurostar's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20dishes%20are%20made%20using%20ingredients%20sourced%20from%20local%20farmers%2C%20growers%2C%20and%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20ordered%20the%20sweet-potato%20falafel%2C%20grilled%20zucchini%2C%20hummus%20with%20Moroccan%20spices%2C%20and%20a%20spelt%2C%20corn%2C%20and%20scallion%20salad.%20His%20dessert%20was%20a%20white-chocolate%20cheesecake%20with%20blackcurrant%20compote.%20My%20prebooked%20gluten-free%20meal%20was%20tender%20chicken%20with%20a%20chickpea%20salad%20followed%20by%20a%20fruit%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20delighted%20once%20we%20tasted%20the%20food%3A%20What%20it%20may%20lack%20in%20presentation%2C%20it%20more%20than%20makes%20up%20for%20in%20flavor.%20Plus%2C%20it%20was%20served%20with%20real%20cutlery%20and%20glassware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeer%2C%20wine%2C%20and%20soft%20drinks%20were%20also%20on%20offer%2C%20and%20we%20chose%20mini%20bottles%20of%20a%20quaffable%20Syrah.%20Just-about-drinkable%20coffee%20and%20tea%20were%20served%20after%20our%20meal.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20train%20took%20us%20right%20into%20a%20famous%20terminal%20in%20Paris.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Buildings%20next%20to%20a%20street%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717bd1b9b3250dbbce92328%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20enjoyed%20walking%20around%20Paris%20on%20foot.%20%3Cp%3EEmily%20Garnham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20journey%20was%20over%20in%20two%20hours%20and%2023%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20train%20goes%20right%20into%20the%20famous%20Gare%20Du%20Nord%20terminal%20in%20central%20Paris%2C%20some%20travelers%20may%20be%20able%20to%20save%20money%20on%20pricey%20transfers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we'd%20only%20brought%20backpacks%20for%20our%20short%20stay%2C%20we%20exited%20the%20station%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20leisurely%2C%20meandering%2050-minute%20stroll%20to%20our%20hotel%20in%20the%203rd%20Arrondissement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20felt%20like%20a%20far%20better%20way%20to%20immerse%20ourselves%20in%20the%20sights%20and%20sounds%20of%20the%20city%20than%20taking%20the%20Metro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20the%20upgraded%20train%20experience%20was%20well%20worth%20the%20extra%20money.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Exterior%20of%20a%20train%20stopped%20at%20a%20glass-ceilinged%20train%20station%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6717bd1b9b3250dbbce92327%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222822%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20would%20upgrade%20again%20for%20an%20enhanced%20Eurostar%20rail%20experience.%20%3Cp%3EEmily%20Garnham%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pricier%20top-tier%20class%20%E2%80%94%20Eurostar%20Premier%20%E2%80%94%20offers%20added%20perks%2C%20the%20best%20being%20that%20tickets%20are%20exchangeable%20and%20refundable%20with%20no%20fee%20up%20to%2048%20hours%20after%20departure.%20Ticket%20holders%20can%20also%20access%20exclusive%20lounges%2C%20skip%20the%20queues%20with%20priority%20ticket%20gates%2C%20and%20take%20more%20luggage%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20perks%20don't%20come%20cheap%3A%20Eurostar%20Premier%20ticket%20costs%20for%20this%20route%20are%20over%20%2