tective%20measures%2C%20such%20as%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20Indian%20goods%2C%20potentially%20adding%20barriers%20for%20key%20Indian%20exports%20like%20automobiles%2C%20wines%2C%20textiles%2C%20and%20pharmaceuticals.%20These%20increases%20could%20make%20Indian%20products%20less%20competitive%20in%20the%20US%2C%20impacting%20revenue%20in%20these%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20Srivastava%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20tougher%20US%20stance%20on%20China%20could%20create%20new%20opportunities%20for%20Indian%20exporters%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bilateral%20trade%20in%20goods%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20stood%20at%20USD%20120%20billion%20in%202023-24%20as%20against%20USD%20129.4%20billion%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20GTRI%20report%20had%20earlier%20stated%20that%20according%20to%20WTO's%20World%20Tariff%20Profiles%202023%2C%20the%20US%20also%20imposes%20high%20duties%20on%20items%20like%20dairy%20products%20(188%20per%20cent)%2C%20Fruits%20and%20vegetables%20(132%20per%20cent)%2C%20cereals%20and%20food%20preparations%20(193%20per%20cent)%2C%20oilseeds%2C%20fats%20and%20oils%20(164%20per%20cent)%2C%20beverages%20and%20tobacco%20(150%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20trade%20expert%20Biswajit%20Dhar%20said%20that%20Trump%20would%20increase%20tariffs%20in%20various%20sectors%20as%20he%20has%20to%20follow%20his%20call%20for%20MAGA%20(Make%20America%20Great%20Again).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Trump%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20enter%20a%20different%20era%20of%20protectionism%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhar%20said%20adding%20sectors%20like%20electronics%20may%20get%20a%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20as%20earlier%20Trump%20has%20walked%20out%20of%20Trans-Pacific%20Partnership%20(TPP)%2C%20there%20could%20be%20dark%20clouds%20on%20IPEF%20(Indo-Pacific%20Economic%20Framework%20for%20Prosperity).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2014-nation%20bloc%20was%20launched%20in%20Tokyo%20by%20the%20US%20and%20other%20Indo-Pacific%20countries%20on%20May%2023%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20us%20see%20what%20he%20does%20with%20IPEF%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhar%20cautioned%20and%20added%20that%20nothing%20is%20expected%20to%20move%20in%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%20(WTO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFederation%20of%20Indian%20Export%20Organisations%20(FIEO)%20DG%20Ajay%20Sahai%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20could%20expect%20Mr%20Trump%20to%20push%20for%20more%20balanced%20trade.%20But%20trade%20disputes%20might%20arise%20around%20tariffs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20by%20the%20increasing%20trend%20of%20protectionism%2C%20Sahai%20said%2C%20the%20same%20would%20continue%20with%20tighter%20immigration%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgneshwar%20Sen%2C%20Partner-Tax%20and%20Economic%20Policy%20(International%20Trade)%2C%20EY%20India%20said%20it%20may%20be%20expected%20that%20the%20US%20will%20use%20high%20tariffs%20strategically%20to%20onshore%20manufacturing%20and%20change%20current%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20could%20face%20higher%20tariffs%20on%20exports%20like%20textiles%2C%20chemicals%2C%20pharma%20and%20auto%2F%20engineering%20products%2C%20Sen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20would%20have%20to%20either%20seek%20alternative%20markets%20(which%20will%20be%20difficult)%20or%20retaliate%20with%20its%20own%20tariffs%20on%20US%20exports.%20Alternately%2C%20we%20must%20be%20ready%20for%20a%20trade%20deal%20that%20is%20attractive%20to%20the%20US%20while%20not%20just%20protecting%20our%20current%20interests%20but%20creating%20newer%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20Srivastava%20said%20that%20Trump%20has%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20outsourcing%2C%20and%20while%20some%20statements%20may%20be%20campaign%20rhetoric%2C%20India%20should%20prepare%20for%20possible%20measures%20affecting%20IT%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EH-1B%20visa%20policies%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20movement%20of%20skilled%20professionals%2C%20especially%20from%20India's%20IT%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump's%20stricter%20immigration%20stance%20could%20lead%20to%20changes%20in%20visa%20rules%2C%20impacting%20Indian%20IT%20professionals%20and%20raising%20costs%20for%20Indian%20IT%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20GTRI%20Founder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%20that%20Trump%20is%20expected%20to%20ease%20labour%20and%20environmental%20standards%2C%20which%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20Indian%20exports%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20would%20likely%20push%20India%20to%20align%20closely%20with%20US%20geopolitical%20aims%2C%20potentially%20expanding%20India's%20role%20as%20an%20alternative%20supplier%20in%20sectors%20like%20electronics%20and%20pharmaceuticals%20but%20potentially%20limiting%20India's%20foreign%20policy%20flexibility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20India's%20increasing%20demand%20for%20advanced%20technology%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20capital%20goods%20from%20the%20US%20opens%20avenues%20for%20expanding%20bilateral%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20FY'2020%20and%20FY'2024%2C%20India's%20merchandise%20exports%20to%20America%20rose%20by%2046%20per%20cent%20from%20USD%2053.1%20billion%20to%20USD%2077.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImports%20from%20the%20US%20also%20grew%20to%20USD%2042.2%20billion%20last%20fiscal%20from%20USD%2035.8%20billion%20in%202019-20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20trade%20in%20services%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20expanded%20from%20USD%2054.1%20billion%20in%202018%20to%20an%20estimated%20USD%2070.5%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20a%2030.3%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20also%20a%20key%20destination%20for%20American%20businesses%20such%20as%20professional%2C%20scientific%2C%20and%20technical%20services%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20IT.%20Washington%20is%20the%20third%20largest%20investor.%20India%20received%20USD%2066.7%20billion%20between%20April%202000%20and%20June%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20buys%20military%20equipment%20and%20Boeings%20worth%20billions%20of%20dollars%20from%20the%20US%20and%20conducts%20its%20over%2090%20per%20cent%20global%20trade%20in%20US%20Dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20firms%20like%20Google%2C%20Facebook%20gather%20Terabytes%20of%20data%20every%20day%20and%20earn%20billions%20of%20advertising%20dollars%20every%20year%20from%20India.%20Amazon%20which%20had%20to%20withdraw%20from%20China%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20online%20retailer%20in%20India.%20The%20US%20earns%20dollars%20from%20India%20from%20various%20engagements%20and%20not%20just%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20Srivastava%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730894580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F5keho7ao_donald-trump_625x300_06_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrumps-america-first-agenda-may-lead-to-tighter-h-1b-visa-rules-experts-6957234%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Donald%20Trump%20all%20set%20to%20become%20US%20president%2C%20Indian%20exporters%20may%20face%20high%20customs%20duties%20for%20goods%20like%20automobiles%2C%20textiles%20and%20pharmaceuticals%20if%20the%20new%20US%20administration%20decides%20to%20pursue%20the%20America%20First'%20agenda%2C%20opined%20trade%20experts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrumps-america-first-agenda-may-lead-to-tighter-h-1b-visa-rules-experts-6957234%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Trump's%20Victory%20Speech%2C%20A%20Shout-Out%20To%20'Bobby'%20Kennedy.%20What%20It%20Could%20Be%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20vic