ke%20of%20the%20larger%20public%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20the%20template%20in%20which%20Pawan%20Kalyan's%20outburst%20against%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20home%20minister%20Anitha%20Vangalapudi%20could%20be%20viewed.%20He%20is%20part%20of%20the%20government%2C%20he%20could%20be%20held%20accountable%20too%20for%20the%20acts%20of%20omission%20and%20commission.%20Yet%2C%20in%20one%20smooth%20stroke%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20dissociate%20himself%20from%20these%20apparent%20failings%20and%20positioned%20himself%20as%20someone%20who%20could%20take%20drastic%20action%20to%20correct%20the%20'wrongs'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20damage-control%20mode%2C%20senior%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20minister%20P.%20Narayana%20said%20that%20as%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20Kalyan%20could%20guide%20and%20instruct%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20cabinet.%20Home%20minister%20Anitha%20said%20he%20had%20not%20called%20her%20incompetent%2C%20but%20he%20had%20in%20fact%20backed%20her%2C%20asking%20her%20to%20become%20more%20aggressive%20in%20her%20stance%20against%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPawan's%20Enviable%20Position%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20was%20Kalyan%20undermining%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20authority%3F%20By%20suggesting%20that%20he%20could%20ask%20for%20and%20take%20charge%20of%20the%20home%20ministry%2C%20he%20is%20indicating%20that%20it%20is%20not%20the%20prerogative%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20alone%20to%20allocate%20portfolios%2C%20and%20that%20Kalyan%20could%20flex%20his%20muscles%20too.%20That%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20positioning%20and%20messaging%20about%20the%20power%20he%20commands%20in%20the%20alliance%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20issue%20is%20the%20reference%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%20Kalyan%20said%20the%20TDP%20government%20should%20take%20a%20cue%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20dealing%20with%20law%20and%20order%20problems.%20Political%20observers%20are%20wondering%20if%20that%20is%20an%20admission%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%20been%20successful%20in%20doing%20something%20that%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20had%20failed%20to%20do.%20Some%20analysts%20see%20in%20this%20an%20open%20admiration%20for%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20announced%20a%20new%20wing%20in%20the%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20which%20he%20called%20the%20Narasimha%20Varahi%20Brigade.%20Its%20task%20was%20to%20take%20on%20and%20challenge%20those%20who%20spoke%20against%20the%20'Sanatana%20Dharma'.%20This%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20has%20been%20very%20vocal%20about%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20asking%20for%20national%20legislation%2C%20a%20national%20organisational%20structure%20and%20funds%20to%20protect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKalyan%2C%20The%20Grassroots%20Champion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalyan%20delivers%20both%20film%20dialogues%20and%20political%20statements%20conveying%20heartfelt%20emotion%20and%20passionate%20commitment%20to%20a%20cause.%20That%20is%20why%20even%20though%20he%20made%20his%20political%20foray%20years%20before%20he%20tasted%20electoral%20success%2C%20the%20frenzy%20he%20evoked%20among%20his%20youthful%20fans%20never%20ebbed.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20his%20political%20messaging%20is%20full%20of%20lofty%20ideals%20and%20is%20aimed%20at%20conveying%20his%20sincerity%20towards%20causes%20he%20has%20declared%20close%20to%20his%20heart.%20Kalyan%20wants%20to%20project%20himself%20as%20the%20grassroots%20man%2C%20using%20sentiment%20and%20emotion%20to%20convey%20that%20his%20heart%20beats%20for%20the%20common%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20will%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20eventually%20emerge%20as%20a%20poster%20boy%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20perhaps%20taking%20on%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20YSRCP%3F%20That%20could%20be%20possible%20on%2