3%A9sum%C3%A9%20to%20match%20each%20job%20description%20but%20instead%20of%20tweaking%20some%20wording%2C%20it%20occasionally%20added%20false%20information%2C%20including%20qualifications%20he%20didn't%20have.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20an%20earlier%20version%20of%20AIHawk%20prevented%20him%20from%20seeing%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20was%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEttinger%20said%20issues%20like%20these%20have%20been%20improved%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20his%20and%20other%20GitHub%20users'%20recommendations.%20He%20said%20the%20tool%20inserts%20fewer%20errors%20and%20that%20users%20are%20now%20able%20to%20access%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20submitted%20for%20each%20job%20to%20check%20for%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20users%20can%20now%20choose%20to%20submit%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20without%20any%20AI%20tweaks%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20tool's%20mass%20application%20benefits%20while%20avoiding%20the%20chance%20of%20errors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEttinger%20estimated%20that%20he's%20applied%20to%20about%20500%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ejobs%20with%20the%20tool%20and%20landed%20a%20few%20interviews.%20While%20he%20hasn't%20found%20a%20job%20yet%2C%20he%20said%20he'll%20continue%20using%20AIHawk%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20more%20traditional%20application%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pretty%20good%20tool%20because%20applying%20to%20jobs%20is%20the%20most%20painstaking%20thing%20for%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b853b1cf-ff0a-4271-af17-6e08b2db6ea1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsing%20the%20tool%20could%20come%20with%20some%20risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETommi%2C%20who%20hopes%20to%20land%20a%20full-time%20data%20engineering%20role%20to%20supplement%20his%20freelance%20work%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eestimates%20he's%20applied%20for%20over%201%2C000%20jobs%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20AIHawk%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20basically%20just%20leave%20it%20on%20autopilot%20applying%20for%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2028-year-old%2C%20who's%20based%20in%20Mexico%20City%2C%20told%20BI.%20Tommi%2C%20whose%20identity%20was%20verified%20by%20BI%20but%20preferred%20to%20use%20his%20first%20name%20due%20to%20fear%20of%20professional%20repercussions%2C%20said%20it's%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20customizing%20materials%20for%20job%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETommi%20estimated%20that%20it%20can%20take%20AIHawk%20between%20three%20and%20six%20hours%20to%20apply%20to%20250%20LinkedIn%20easy-apply%20positions%2C%20which%20he%20said%20is%20roughly%20the%20limit%20LinkedIn%20allows%20per%20day.%20He%20said%20he's%20only%20applied%20for%20jobs%20using%20his%20own%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20letting%20the%20tool%20tweak%20it%20%E2%80%94%20because%20he's%20concerned%20it%20could%20add%20false%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Tommi%20hasn't%20been%20hired%20yet%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20averaging%20about%20one%20interview%20and%20three%20pre-interview%20examinations%20a%20week.%20He%20plans%20to%20continue%20using%20AIHawk%2C%20though%20he%20has%20some%20concerns%20that%20he%20could%20face%20repercussions%20from%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20concern%20among%20Tommi%20and%20other%20AIHawk%20users%20originated%20in%20September%20when%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELinkedIn%20restricted%20Elia%20from%20using%20the%20platform.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELinkedIn%20did%20not%20specifically%20answer%20a%20question%20about%20why%20Elia's%20account%20has%20been%20restricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAIHawk%20users%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20tool%20could%20be%20difficult%20for%20a%20platform%20like%20LinkedIn%20to%20detect%20because%20its%20scrolling%20and%20speed%20mimic%20the%20way%20people%20typically%20apply%20for%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexander%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAlonso%2C%20chief%20data%20and%20insights%20officer%20at%20the%20Society%20for%20Human%20Resource%20Management%2C%20said%20he%20thinks%20most%20HR%20departments%20have%20limited%20insight%20into%20how%20much%20their%20applicants%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20craft%20and%20submit%20their%20applications%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20technological%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20false%20information%20on%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20cover%20letters%20is%20a%20real%20concern%20for%20departments%2C%20but%20there%20is%20likely%20less%20worry%20about%20tools%20that%20help%20people%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emass-apply%20for%20jobs%20due%20to%20some%20of%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20having%20a%20positive%20effect%20in%20that%20you're%20seeing%20a%20broader%20pool%20of%20people%20come%20to%20your%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Alonso%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20using%20AIHawk%20to%20apply%20for%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20notoriety%20that%20came%20with%20the%20tool's%20popularity%20on%20Github%20%E2%80%94%20Elia%20saw%20an%20uptick%20in%20interest%20from%20recruiters.%20Instead%20of%20taking%20a%20job%2C%20he%20teamed%20up%20with%20six%20cofounders%20to%20launch%20AIHawk.co%2C%20which%20he%20hopes%20to%20develop%20into%20a%20job%20search%20platform%20for%20candidates%20and%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElia%20said%20that%20he's%20never%20encouraged%20people%20to%20use%20AIHawk%20to%20apply%20for%20jobs.%20The%20AIHawk%20GitHub%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ffeder-cr%2FAuto_Jobs_Applier_AIHawk%3Ftab%3Dreadme-ov-file%26ref%3D404media.co%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epage%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20a%20disclaimer%20that%20the%20tool%20is%20intended%20for%20education%20purposes%20only%20and%20advises%20users%20to%20comply%20with%20a%20platform's%20terms%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuilherme%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20based%20in%20Brazil%2C%20said%20he's%20applied%20to%20more%20than%20500%20jobs%20with%20AIHawk%20and%20had%20six%20interviews.%20While%20he%20hasn't%20received%20a%20job%20offer%20yet%2C%20he's%20hopeful%20the%20tool%20will%20help%20him%20reach%20more%20employers.%20Guilherme%2C%20whose%20identity%20was%20verified%20by%20BI%20but%20asked%20to%20use%20a%20pseudonym%2C%20was%20laid%20off%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20struggling%20financially%20for%20over%20a%20year%20at%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20and%20comfortable%20sharing%20your%20story%20with%20a%20reporter%3F%20Did%20an%20AI%20job%20tool%20help%20you%20land%20a%20job%20recently%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EPlease%20fill%20out%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScLu79elRbqrSr2cMp5JcqOQJheuCX77QuJqLYr9qEzH3t4Qw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faihawk-applies-jobs-for-you-linkedin-risks-inaccuracies-mistakes-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730890981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672a621a192f525898563106%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faihawk-applies-jobs-for-you-linkedin-risks-inaccuracies-mistakes-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20tool%20called%20AIHawk%20is%20helping%20some%20job%20seekers%20apply%20for%20hundreds%20of%20jobs%20a%20day%20on%20LinkedIn.%20But%20users%20said%20there%20are%20risks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A85%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faihawk-applies-jobs-for-you-linkedin-risks-inaccuracies-mistakes-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%