r%20or%20self-declaration%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20known%20when%20and%20from%20where%20these%20pictures%20were%20taken%2C%20so%20how%20can%20we%20tell%3F%26quot%3B%20shot%20back%20the%20lawyer%20representing%20the%20NCP.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20told%20Ajit%20Pawar%20that%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20earlier%20order%20will%20be%20contempt%20of%20the%20court.%20Today%2C%20the%20judges%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIssue%20public%20notices%20in%20newspapers%20with%20Marathi%2C%20Hindi%20and%20English%20versions%20and%20show%20it%20to%20the%20court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730889780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F005arkp_sharad-pawar-ajit-pawar-ani_625x300_07_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawar-group-gets-36-hours-to-publish-clock-symbol-disclaimer-6956698%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party's%20Ajit%20Pawar%20will%20continue%20to%20use%20the%20clock%20symbol%20but%20will%20have%20to%20give%20a%20declaration%20within%2036%20hours%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20still%20under%20the%20consideration%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawar-group-gets-36-hours-to-publish-clock-symbol-disclaimer-6956698%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20Pakistan%20spinner%20hails%20MS%20Dhoni%20as%20best%20captain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730889768000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115016147%2Cimgsize-30538.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fcool-calm-and-successful-pakistan-spinner-hails-ms-dhoni-as-best-captain%2Farticleshow%2F115016214.cms%22%2C%22summ