%3Bbulldozer%20justice%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20term%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20demolishing%20properties%20belonging%20to%20people%20accused%20in%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20today%20that%20the%20demolition%20in%20this%20case%20was%20carried%20out%20without%20any%20notice.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20(that)%20demolition%20was%20high-handed%20and%20without%20the%20authority%20of%20law.%20The%20petitioner%20states%20the%20demolition%20was%20only%20(carried%20out)%20because%20the%20petitioner%20had%20flagged%20irregularities%20in%20road%20construction%20in%20a%20newspaper%20report.%20Such%20action%20by%20the%20state%20cannot%20be%20countenanced%20and%20when%20dealing%20with%20private%20property%2C%20law%20has%20to%20be%20followed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20had%20said%20the%20petitioner%20had%20encroached%20on%20public%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20say%20that%20he%20was%20an%20encroacher%20of%203.7%20sq%20m.%20We%20take%20it%2C%20we%20are%20not%20giving%20him%20a%20certificate%20for%20it%2C%20but%20how%20can%20you%20start%20demolishing%20people's%20houses%20like%20that%3F%20This%20is%20lawlessness...%20walking%20into%20somebody's%20house...%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Pardiwala%2C%20also%20part%20of%20the%20three-judge%20bench%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20come%20with%20bulldozers%20and%20demolish%20houses%20overnight.%20You%20don't%20give%20time%20to%20family%20to%20vacate.%20What%20about%20the%20household%20articles%3F%20There%20has%20to%20be%20due%20process%20followed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20case%20documents%20show%20that%20the%20petitioner%20was%20not%20issued%20a%20notice.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20affidavit%20that%20says%20no%20notice%20was%20issued%2C%20you%20only%20went%20to%20the%20site%20and%20informed%20the%20people%20through%20loudspeaker.%20You%20can't%20just%20with%20a%20beat%20of%20a%20drum%20tell%20people%20to%20vacate%20houses%20and%20demolish%20them.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20proper%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanth%20government%20to%20pay%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20as%20compensation.%20It%20also%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20conduct%20an%20inquiry%20and%20take%20action%20against%20officers%20responsible%20for%20the%20illegal%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20laid%20down%20guidelines%20the%20state%20government%20must%20follow%20in%20such%20cases%3A%20they%20must%20ascertain%20the%20width%20of%20the%20road%2C%20issue%20notice%20to%20remove%20encroachment%2C%20decide%20on%20any%20objections%20and%20give%20reasonable%20time%20to%20remove%20the%20encroachment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730889420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-uttar-pradesh-this-is-lawlessness-top-court-raps-uttar-pradesh-for-illegal-demolition-6956844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pulling%20up%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20for%20demolishing%20homes%20without%20due%20process%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20homes%20cannot%20be%20razed%20overnight%20and%20families%20must%20be%20given%20time%20to%20vacate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-uttar-pradesh-this-is-lawlessness-top-court-raps-uttar-pradesh-for-illegal-demolition-6956844%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CNN%E2%80%99s%20Van%20Jones%20Chokes%20Up%20as%20He%20Calls%20Trump%20Victory%20a%20%E2%80%98Nightmare%E2%80%99%3A%20Kamala%20Harris%20Supporters%20Are%20%E2%80%98Going%20to%20Be%20Terrified%E2%80%99%22%2C%22conte