rovocative-speech-in-bengal-6956820%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Move%20Over%2C%20Rupert%20Murdoch.%20Elon%20Musk%20Is%20The%20New%20Master%20Of%20Perception%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeven%20decades%20ago%2C%20a%20young%20Rupert%20Murdoch%20inherited%20a%20newspaper%20in%20Australia.%20The%20family-run%20publication%20would%20transform%20over%20the%20decades%20into%20the%20world's%20most%20influential%20media%20empire%2C%20guiding%20political%20direction%20in%20multiple%20countries.%20However%2C%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20the%20perception%20war%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20West%2C%20is%20largely%20fought%20on%20social%20media.%20Today%2C%20Murdoch%20is%20retired%20at%2093%2C%20and%20a%20new%20figure%20has%20risen%20as%20the%20master%20of%20perception%3A%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20control%20over%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20grants%20him%20a%20platform%20with%20unparalleled%20influence%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20broadcast%20messages%20and%20shape%20opinions%20with%20an%20audience%20numbering%20in%20the%20hundreds%20of%20millions.%20As%20Musk%20aligns%20his%20views%20with%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%26quot%3B%20(MAGA)%20movement%2C%20he%20amplifies%20far-right%20rhetoric%20much%20like%20Murdoch%20once%20did.%20But%20Musk's%20methods%20and%20ambitions%20differ%20from%20those%20of%20his%20predecessor.%20His%20platform%2C%20X%2C%20functions%20as%20a%20digital%20megaphone%20broadcasting%20ideas%20that%20reach%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20unlike%20Murdoch's%20newspapers%2C%20news%20channels%20or%20radio%20stations%20that%20catered%20to%20a%20specific%20subscriber%20base.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20Musk's%20influence%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20first%20look%20at%20Murdoch's%20legacy.%20Fox%20News%2C%20his%20crowning%20achievement%2C%20became%20a%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%20and%20a%20centre%20of%20conservative%20ideology%20in%20the%20US.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20Murdoch's%20influence%20over%20the%20Republicans%20has%20waned.%20Attempts%20to%20make%20Trump%20politically%20irrelevant%20were%20unsuccessful%2C%20and%20as%20seen%20in%20the%202024%20US%20Presidential%20election%20results%2C%20Trump's%20grip%20on%20the%20party%20has%20never%20been%20stronger.%20With%20Murdoch's%20declining%20control%2C%20another%20figure%20has%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump%20sailed%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld%2Felections%5C%22%3E2024%20presidential%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Musk%20emerged%20as%20a%20powerful%20and%20vocal%20ally.%20Musk's%20acquisition%20of%20X%20has%20allowed%20him%20to%20shape%20the%20information%20ecosystem%20in%20ways%20that%20align%20with%20his%20ideology.%20Musk's%20controversial%20moderation%20policy%20changes%20have%20weakened%20X's%20ability%20to%20regulate%20harmful%20content%2C%20amplifying%20incendiary%20rhetoric%20and%20spreading%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngaging%20with%20far-right%20accounts%2C%20the%20self-proclaimed%20%26quot%3Bfree%20speech%20absolutist%26quot%3B%20Musk%20has%20inadvertently%20provided%20these%20figures%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20algorithm%20booster%2C%26quot%3B%20amplifying%20their%20reach%20and%20influence%20on%20the%20platform.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Musk%2C%20X%20is%20more%20than%20a%20platform%2C%20it's%20a%20tool%20to%20challenge%20the%20establishment%2C%20and%20rally%20support%20for%20conservative%20ideals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20involvement%20in%20US%20politics%20raised%20alarm%20bells%20for%20election%20officials%20across%20critical%20battleground%20states%20like%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Michigan%2C%20and%20Arizona%20-%20three%20states%20where%20Trump%20is%20expected%20to%20win.%20The%20spread%20of%20misinformation%20has%20surged%20as%20X%2C%20under%20Musk's%20leadership%2C%20has%20become%20a%20key%20conduit%20for%20false%20narratives%