r%20these%20children%20even%20after%20they%20graduated%20from%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20an%20after-school%20programme%20for%20our%20alumni.%20Part-time%20teachers%20conduct%20special%20classes%20for%20students%20from%20Classes%208%20to%2012%20over%20the%20weekend.%20We%20provide%20them%20with%20all%20the%20necessary%20tools%20they%20need%20to%20succeed.%20We%20have%20partnered%20with%20local%20high%20schools%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20transition%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Srinivasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20also%20covers%20students%E2%80%99%20college%20fees%2C%20provides%20laptops%20for%20their%20studies%2C%20and%20more.%20Thanks%20to%20these%20efforts%2C%20many%20students%20have%20completed%20their%20graduation.%20Some%20have%20become%20engineers%2C%20others%20are%20training%20to%20become%20chartered%20accountants%20or%20entering%20finance%2C%20one%20is%20pursuing%20an%20MBBS%2C%20and%20Pavan%20is%20even%20working%20toward%20a%20doctorate.%20Several%20have%20completed%20industrial%20training%20and%20now%20work%20with%20reputable%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20students%20reach%20Class%207%2C%20the%20alumni%20director%20discusses%20their%20preferred%20high%20schools%20and%20helps%20arrange%20admissions.%20By%20Class%2010%2C%20students%20receive%20career%20counselling%20and%20are%20asked%20to%20select%20their%20top%20three%20colleges%2C%20with%20TCF%20assisting%20in%20securing%20their%20placements.%20The%20foundation%20also%20offers%20personal%20coaching%20in%20subjects%20like%20maths%2C%20science%2C%20economics%2C%20statistics%2C%20business%20studies%2C%20computer%20skills%20and%20English%20to%20support%20students%20after%20school%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20cycle%3A%20Education%20as%20a%20pathway%20out%20of%20poverty%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20break%20the%20shackles%20of%20poverty.%20A%20house-help%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20follow%20h