0%E2%80%93%20Reality%20Stars%2C%20although%20well-received%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%20commercially.%20Just%2025%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20cope%20with%20this%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20toast%20of%20MTV.%20Everyone%20hyped%20me%20up%20and%20pushed%20me.%20When%20the%20series%20was%20launched%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20there%20was%20complete%20silence.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20tools%20or%20resources%20to%20handle%20the%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20retrospect%2C%20he%20acknowledges%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20handle%20it%20well.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20anxious%20for%20almost%20three%20to%20four%20months.%20To%20cope%2C%20I%20buried%20myself%20in%20work%20and%20started%20using%20my%20subsequent%20wins%20as%20a%20distraction.%20I%20kept%20telling%20myself%20that%20I%20was%20fine%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits%20candidly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESociety%20often%20fails%20to%20teach%20us%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20handle%20failure%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Nikhil%20continued%20to%20work%2C%20soon%20landing%20his%20dream%20job%20at%20Yash%20Raj%20Films%20(YRF).%20He%20led%20their%20youth%20wing%2C%20Y-Films%2C%20and%20quickly%20became%20the%20general%20manager%20at%20YRF.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20produced%20many%20hit%20web%20series%2C%20seemingly%20setting%20him%20on%20an%20ideal%20career%20path.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20was%20a%20visiting%20professor%20at%20Jai%20Hind%20College%2C%20host%20of%20a%20YouTube%20show%20with%20Film%20Companion%2C%20and%20had%20everything%20he%20dreamed%20of%3B%20he%20was%20not%20even%2030%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20while%20he%20excelled%20at%20work%2C%20he%20was%20quietly%20battling%20anxiety%20without%20knowing%20what%20it%20was.%20He%20experienced%20panic%20attacks%20and%20breakdowns%20at%20work%20and%20home%20but%20kept%20pushing%20himself.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20out%20of%20bed%2C%20and%20often%20found%20himself%20sweating%20uncontrollably.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20fragile%20and%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20breaking%2C%20leading%20to%20self%20doubt.%20I%20used%20to%20think%20that%20I%20was%20a%20terrible%20employee.%20Sometimes%2C%20during%20meetings%2C%20I%20would%20have%20panic%20attacks%20and%20had%20to%20go%20out%20to%20gather%20myself%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20I%20just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20was%20happening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20he%20experienced%20a%20massive%20anxiety%20attack%20and%20feared%20something%20was%20wrong%20with%20his%20heart.%20Like%20many%2C%20Nikhil%20experienced%20his%20anxiety%20manifest%20as%20physical%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20heart%20raced%20constantly.%20I%20felt%20breathless%2C%20as%20if%20I%20were%20on%20a%20plane%20experiencing%20turbulence%2C%20convinced%20everything%20was%20about%20to%20come%20crashing%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBattle%20with%20anxiety%3A%20Taking%20a%20career%20break%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20enduring%20these%20symptoms%20for%20nine%20months%2C%20he%20finally%20visited%20a%20doctor%20for%20a%20p