n%20say%20with%20certainty%20that%20going%20to%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20doorsteps%20with%20services%20makes%20a%20difference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20an%20observation%20of%20the%20uptick%20in%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20seek%20assistance%20in%20family%20planning%20and%20opt%20for%20sterilisation%20procedures%20at%20the%20centre.%20Consulting%20gynaecologist%20Dr%20Shreya%20Prabhoo%20reasons%20this%20increase.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20starting%20to%20become%20more%20cognisant%20of%20family%20planning.%20Earlier%20people%20were%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20female%20sterilisation%20was%20the%20only%20approach.%20Male%20sterilisation%20is%20a%20big%20taboo%20in%20our%20society%2C%20you%20see.%20It%20is%20assumed%20that%20the%20man%20will%20lose%20his%20libido%20or%20%E2%80%98manhood%E2%80%99%20after%20a%20vasectomy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20through%20extensive%20education%20that%20dispels%20these%20misconceptions%2C%20the%20doctors%20are%20starting%20to%20see%20a%20shift%20in%20attitudes.%20The%20statistics%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Andheri%20centre%20has%20completed%2055%2C000%20family%20planning%20surgeries%20%E2%80%94%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20these%20mindset%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuality%20healthcare%20at%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20doorstep%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20state-of-the-art%20services%20and%20consultations%20are%20made%20available%20to%20the%20patients%20who%20head%20to%20the%20L%26amp%3BT%20centres%2C%20there%20was%20a%20burgeoning%20need%20to%20extend%20the%20same%20to%20those%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20this%20privilege.%20This%20gap%20is%20bridged%20by%20the%20Mobile%20Health%20Units%2C%20which%20take%20medical%20services%20to%20the%20urban%2C%20peri-urban%2C%20as%20well%20as%20far-flung%20rural%20and%20tribal%20poor%2C%20explains%20Dahlia%20Sengupta%2C%20a%20volunteer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2015%20years%20Sengupta%20has%20co-ordinat